name: Highhorn
description: Many times the light of Alva Merris has passed by this place since the horn of Highhorn has barked its call across the Midland marches in search of allies.   Ann-Maela Arranoss looked west as the sun dipped below the ragged skyline and the long shadows turned to dusk and then to darkness. Her left hand dropped to the pommel of her longsword and she shuddered at the memory of the knights of Deadwater.  They had come, and she had stopped them with black powder and the loss of half her castle.
